---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'May 13, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy · Viva Wellness Co."
  description="How Viva Wellness Co. collects, uses, and protects your information. Plain-language privacy practices for our concierge telehealth website."
>

  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container legal-hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">· Privacy</span>
      <h1 class="legal-hero__title">
        Your data, <span class="italic-display">your control.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Plain language. No dark patterns. Here is exactly what we collect, why,
        and how to opt out at any time.
      </p>
      <p class="legal-hero__updated">Last updated · {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="legal-body">
    <div class="container legal-body__inner">

      <div class="legal-callout">
        <strong>The short version.</strong>
        We collect contact details when you fill out a form on this site, plus
        the answers you give to our protocol-match quiz. We use that information
        to email you our eBook, reply to your inquiry, and occasionally send you
        new articles. We never sell it. You can unsubscribe at any time.
      </div>

      <h2 class="legal-h">What we collect</h2>
      <p>
        From the <a href="/contact">contact page</a> and the home-page
        protocol-match quiz, we collect the information you give us: your name,
        email address, phone number (optional), the answers you choose in the
        quiz, and any free-text message you send.
      </p>
      <p>
        We also automatically receive limited technical information: which page
        referred you (the HTTP <em>Referer</em> header) and the campaign tags in
        your URL (UTM parameters). This is the same information any website
        receives by default. We use it to understand which articles and ads are
        useful so we can write more of what works.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do <strong>not</strong> use analytics cookies on this site. We do
        not track you across other websites.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">How we use it</h2>
      <p>
        To deliver the Precision Hormone &amp; Peptide Therapy eBook to the
        email you provided, reply to questions you ask us, and follow up if
        Liliana wants to introduce a relevant new article or protocol. That is
        the entire scope of marketing communication from this website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Service providers we use</h2>
      <ul class="legal-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Resend</strong> · sends our transactional email (eBook
          delivery and inquiry replies). Your name and email pass through their
          systems for that purpose.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Cloudflare</strong> · hosts this website. They process the
          basic server logs and DDoS protection data that any web host needs.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>GlossGenius</strong> · handles appointment booking and
          payments when you book a visit. They have their own privacy policy
          and we never see your full card details.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="legal-h">A note on health information</h2>
      <p>
        This website does <strong>not</strong> collect protected health
        information (PHI). The quiz and contact forms are for marketing and
        lead intake only. Once you become a patient, all clinical communication
        moves into our HIPAA-compliant patient portal (Charm Health). Lab
        orders, medication shipments, dose adjustments, and provider messaging
        all happen there, never through this website or generic email.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Email opt-out</h2>
      <p>
        Every email we send includes an unsubscribe link. You can also email
        <a href="mailto:info@vivawellnessco.com">info@vivawellnessco.com</a>
        and ask us to remove you from any list, and we will do so within one
        business day.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Children</h2>
      <p>
        Our services are for adults eighteen and older. We do not knowingly
        collect information from anyone under eighteen.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Updates</h2>
      <p>
        If we change how we handle information, we will update this page and
        revise the date at the top. Material changes get an email to anyone on
        our list.
      </p>

      <h2 class="legal-h">Questions</h2>
      <p>
        Email <a href="mailto:info@vivawellnessco.com">info@vivawellnessco.com</a>
        or call <a href="tel:+17372107283">(737) 210-7283</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="legal-foot">
        Viva Wellness Co. · 5900 Balcones Dr #19640, Austin, TX 78731
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    padding: clamp(5rem, 11vw, 9rem) 0 clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .legal-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(800px 500px at 75% 0%, rgba(201, 120, 58, 0.14), transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .legal-hero__inner { position: relative; max-width: 70ch; }
  .legal-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7vw, 5.5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-hero__title .italic-display { color: var(--bronze-bright); }
  .legal-hero__updated {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mute);
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    padding-top: 1.2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .legal-body { padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 clamp(5rem, 10vw, 8rem); }
  .legal-body__inner { max-width: 70ch; margin: 0 auto; }

  .legal-callout {
    background: var(--ink-2);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--bronze);
    padding: 1.6rem 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.9);
  }
  .legal-callout strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--bronze);
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .legal-h {
    font-family: var(--font-display-italic);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.6vw, 1.9rem);
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    margin: 2.8rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--paper);
  }
  .legal-body p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    max-width: none;
  }
  .legal-body a {
    color: var(--bronze);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(201, 120, 58, 0.4);
    transition: color 200ms var(--ease), border-color 200ms var(--ease);
  }
  .legal-body a:hover {
    color: var(--bronze-bright);
    border-color: var(--bronze-bright);
  }
  .legal-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.9rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1.5rem;
  }
  .legal-list li {
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
    color: rgba(245, 241, 234, 0.85);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .legal-list li::before {
    content: '·';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--bronze);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .legal-list strong { color: var(--paper); }

  .legal-foot {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--mute);
  }
</style>
